What is Lorem Ipsum?

Lorem Ipsum are mixed texts used in the typesetting and printing industry. Lorem Ipsum is a typeface by an unknown printer. It has been used as industry standard dummy texts since the 1500s, when he took a gallery of scripts and scrambled them to create a sample book. Not only did it survive for five hundred years, it also migrated to electronic typesetting, much unchanged.
